theorem rel_map_quotient_mk {n : ℕ} (r : L.relations n) (x : fin n → M) :
    (rel_map r fun i => «expr⟦ ⟧» (x i)) ↔ @rel_map _ _ ps.to_structure _ r x :=
  by
  change quotient.lift (@rel_map L M ps.to_structure n r) prestructure.rel_equiv (quotient.fin_choice _) ↔ _
  rw [quotient.fin_choice_eq, quotient.lift_mk]
#align rel_map_quotient_mk rel_map_quotient_mk

theorem term.realize_quotient_mk {β : Type _} (t : L.term β) (x : β → M) :
    (t.realize fun i => «expr⟦ ⟧» (x i)) = «expr⟦ ⟧» (@term.realize _ _ ps.to_structure _ x t) :=
  by
  induction' t with _ _ _ _ ih
  · rfl
  · simp only [ih, fun_map_quotient_mk, term.realize]

    (fun_map f fun i => «expr⟦ ⟧» (x i)) = «expr⟦ ⟧» (@fun_map _ _ ps.to_structure _ f x) :=
